title: No Goddess, no!
description: Yoon Heeji is serving as the nation’s current goddess, granting wishes to those that pray to her. But being a goddess isn’t all it’s cracked up to be: there’s paparazzi, constant criticisms from the public, and, well... granting wishes isn’t so easy, either. As Heeji soon discovers, sometimes satisfying a wish client means having to go further than you ever planned...
